name: Export your Corsizio events to Google Sheets
description: This Template helps you export your Corsizio events. At the specified time interval, Make will automatically export your Corsizio events to Google Sheets. The template uses [this example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10Uzpiee_kkBXdEyqecsWAT3KUvqkD8g4cM7z5Ivn0uA/edit?usp=sharing).
